<p begin="2367100000t" end="2436300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">めざすさきはふかく　まっすぐにまよいこむ</p>
<p begin="2367100000t" end="2436300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">目指す先は深く まっすぐに迷い込む</p>
