<p begin="2842600000t" end="2905600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">心目中的憧憬 将永远不再停下脚步</p>
<p begin="2980200000t" end="3020300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">基地</p>
<p begin="2980200000t" end="3020300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">Seeker Camp</p>
<p begin="3028300000t" end="3070300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">真没想到 还能再见到这枚笛子啊</p>
<p begin="3150300000t" end="3191900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">请问 您就是奥森小姐吧</p>
<p begin="3195700000t" end="3218200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">发现这个笛子的人</p>
<p begin="3255100000t" end="3293000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">是啊 我就是奥森</p>
<p begin="3295200000t" end="3313300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">那…那个</p>
<p begin="3318000000t" end="3348600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">多谢您的救命之恩</p>
<p begin="3371200000t" end="3389900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">我听领班说了</p>
<p begin="3395300000t" end="3435800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">出生在阿比斯内部的我 被放入了免除诅咒之笼</p>
<p begin="3439200000t" end="3480700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">之后是您和妈妈一起 把我搬到了地面</p>
<p begin="3487500000t" end="3508100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">哦 那东西啊</p>
<p begin="3513400000t" end="3530800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">重得要命</p>
<p begin="3530800000t" end="3566200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">途中有好几次 都想把它扔了</p>
<p begin="3570700000t" end="3619900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">不堪回首啊 把宝贵的钟都给丢下了</p>
<p begin="3648800000t" end="3692300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">要是抛下你 那小鬼或许就会跟我一起来了</p>
<p begin="3695100000t" end="3720800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">真是令人后悔啊</p>
<p begin="3766100000t" end="3778400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">师尊</p>
<p begin="3815300000t" end="3838400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">你是赤笛对吧</p>
<p begin="3842500000t" end="3878600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">真是不乖 怎么能跑到这儿来呢</p>
<p begin="3908100000t" end="3938700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">因为妈妈在叫我</p>
<p begin="3960500000t" end="3998700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">于是决定 跟雷古一起去奈落之底</p>
<p begin="4004500000t" end="4036000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">所以…只要问完妈妈的事</p>
<p begin="4036000000t" end="4065900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">我们立刻就离开 拜托了</p>
<p begin="4078200000t" end="4110700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">啊 是么 是这样啊</p>
<p begin="4122800000t" end="4172600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">这能算是你们来到这里的正当理由么</p>
<p begin="4180900000t" end="4200700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">对…对不起</p>
<p begin="4222100000t" end="4270600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">话虽如此 区区赤笛是怎么撑到这里的</p>
<p begin="4270600000t" end="4291600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">我倒是挺感兴趣</p>
<p begin="4295800000t" end="4306500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">玛鲁鲁库</p>
<p begin="4310700000t" end="4329100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">是 师尊</p>
<p begin="4335900000t" end="4361600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">你来听他们讲吧</p>
<p begin="4368400000t" end="4381900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">我吗</p>
<p begin="4406500000t" end="4438800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">都是小孩 比较好说话吧</p>
<p begin="4461100000t" end="4497400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">我还有事要做呢</p>
<p begin="4504300000t" end="4529300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">有什么话 等明天再听</p>
<p begin="4554600000t" end="4578200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">两位 请拿着这个</p>
<p begin="4589300000t" end="4602000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">苍笛</p>
<p begin="4606100000t" end="4629400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">暂时给你们拿着</p>
<p begin="4631100000t" end="4650800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">不然其他探窟家来了</p>
<p begin="4650800000t" end="4704100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">还要一遍遍解释为什么赤笛会在这里 也太麻烦了</p>
<p begin="4708300000t" end="4738700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">作为担保 这个我就先收下了</p>
<p begin="4744500000t" end="4776300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">离开时用苍笛来换</p>
<p begin="4785100000t" end="4808000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">今天就住下吧</p>
<p begin="4809900000t" end="4839600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">记得好好洗个澡</p>
<p begin="4841900000t" end="4868900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">一身呕吐味 太恶心了</p>
<p begin="4926400000t" end="4952300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">先带你们瞧瞧这里吧</p>
<p begin="4985900000t" end="5041100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">这座监视基地是利用大波尔塔树的空洞建成的</p>
<p begin="4985900000t" end="5041100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">Seeker Camp</p>
<p begin="5051000000t" end="5103600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">如今依然在内部逐渐扩张 进行增筑</p>
<p begin="5109600000t" end="5127890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">据说大波尔塔的树根</p>
<p begin="5127890000t" end="5168700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">一直延伸到阿比斯之外 远至海底呢</p>
<p begin="5170800000t" end="5190490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">有人证实过吗</p>
<p begin="5192800000t" end="5208400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">似乎只是猜测</p>
<p begin="5215590000t" end="5242600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">觉得它是吸收了海底囤积的营养</p>
<p begin="5242600000t" end="5278600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">所以即使从力场获取的光照较少 依然能茁壮成长</p>
<p begin="5288800000t" end="5335000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">瞧 比如这边的墙壁 就是空洞的内侧</p>
<p begin="5343200000t" end="5383900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">长太大不会缠在一起吗</p>
<p begin="5440800000t" end="5459900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">就用这里吧</p>
<p begin="5530400000t" end="5553000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">浴室在那边</p>
<p begin="5556400000t" end="5584100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">其实本来是清洗遗物的地方</p>
<p begin="5589700000t" end="5624100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">我这就去 去洗干净</p>
<p begin="5674400000t" end="5714200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">那是不屈之花…永恒香吧</p>
<p begin="5717400000t" end="5738000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">真是到处都有啊</p>
<p begin="5741400000t" end="5773000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">雷古明明是机器人 真是不可思议啊</p>
<p begin="5782500000t" end="5814600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">在听莉可说起之前 我都以为你是人呢</p>
<p begin="5819000000t" end="5858100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">所以 胳膊伸长的时候 我还吓了一跳</p>
<p begin="5858100000t" end="5896600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">其实我也没什么身为机器人的自觉</p>
<p begin="5903000000t" end="5923200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">甚至不知道自己是什么人</p>
<p begin="5961500000t" end="5973200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">怎么了</p>
<p begin="5975700000t" end="6001600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">你叫玛鲁鲁库 对吧</p>
<p begin="6001600000t" end="6007700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">是的</p>
<p begin="6012500000t" end="6052000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">其实有件事 我也正感到疑惑</p>
<p begin="6055800000t" end="6066700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">什么事</p>
<p begin="6074500000t" end="6102100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">只要我知道 一定回答你</p>
<p begin="6102100000t" end="6137100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">那个…你是女孩子吗</p>
<p begin="6269300000t" end="6282300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">好冷</p>
<p begin="6297000000t" end="6331200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">原来如此 你也不容易啊</p>
<p begin="6337300000t" end="6356100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">我们都吃了不少苦啊</p>
<p begin="6375400000t" end="6421500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">没有啦雷古 我可没被那样对待过</p>
<p begin="6421500000t" end="6451400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">哎呀 你们已经这么要好了</p>
<p begin="6471200000t" end="6501200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">抱歉 雷古 找东西帮我擦擦</p>
<p begin="6531000000t" end="6551300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">我去找干净衣服</p>
<p begin="6659100000t" end="6702800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">肚子饿了吧 抱歉只有些剩菜…</p>
<p begin="6719000000t" end="6769700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">玛鲁鲁库明明跟我差不多大 却已经是苍笛了啊</p>
<p begin="6788800000t" end="6818700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">一般必须15岁以上才能当苍笛</p>
<p begin="6826600000t" end="6866600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">但我是白笛的直传弟子 算是破例吧</p>
<p begin="6882900000t" end="6926700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">我因故倒在路上时 被师尊收留</p>
<p begin="6935900000t" end="6959000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">之后就一直都在这里</p>
<p begin="6963600000t" end="6990600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">咦 不回地面吗</p>
<p begin="6990600000t" end="7039300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">我对日光比较敏感 无法在地面上生活</p>
<p begin="7050200000t" end="7064700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">是这样啊</p>
<p begin="7064700000t" end="7085800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">好了 快吃吧</p>
<p begin="7108200000t" end="7119400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">我不客气了</p>
<p begin="7171000000t" end="7203400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">师尊在收留我之后</p>
<p begin="7203400000t" end="7237200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">就主动承担下了监视基地的戍人之任</p>
<p begin="7203400000t" end="7237200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">Seeker Camp</p>
<p begin="7253600000t" end="7291800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">说是这样就不用时常返回地面了</p>
<p begin="7297000000t" end="7355900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">这话当然也有几分真心 但她是真的很为我着想</p>
<p begin="7367900000t" end="7414900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">虽然看上去挺可怕的 但真是个好师傅啊</p>
<p begin="7434800000t" end="7452200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">嗯 是呀</p>
<p begin="7678600000t" end="7691200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">话说 玛鲁鲁库</p>
<p begin="7700400000t" end="7709500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">有什么事呢</p>
<p begin="7719300000t" end="7746200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">这屋里的遗物都是怎么回事</p>
<p begin="7752900000t" end="7776300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">莉可都开始随便摆弄了</p>
<p begin="7785500000t" end="7799800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">不要紧的</p>
<p begin="7808400000t" end="7838400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">那都是不会运到地面去的东西</p>
<p begin="7850100000t" end="7906400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">在这附近发掘并甄别之后留下的 都是四级遗物</p>
<p begin="7915800000t" end="7935700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">这是四级遗物啊</p>
<p begin="7944100000t" end="7958100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">雷古你快看</p>
<p begin="7975900000t" end="7996800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">这是我的太阳玉</p>
<p begin="8007600000t" end="8049000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">虽然很像 但这些的形状更加复杂</p>
<p begin="8054100000t" end="8113000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">很多遗物都是越到深层 其形状就越是复杂</p>
<p begin="8129800000t" end="8177900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">这附近开采的遗物 仍有4成都是卵形的</p>
<p begin="8180400000t" end="8222600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">明明是古代人用的道具 真是不可思议啊</p>
<p begin="8226700000t" end="8258400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">好棒呀 我也想挖</p>
<p begin="8274300000t" end="8309300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">要是能住更久的话 倒是确实可以去探窟</p>
<p begin="8315900000t" end="8351800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">对了 我去拜托师尊吧</p>
<p begin="8356800000t" end="8389800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">就多留一段时间 去探窟什么的也好呀</p>
<p begin="8403900000t" end="8414900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">可以吗</p>
<p begin="8414900000t" end="8448700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">头一次有年龄相仿的孩子来这里</p>
<p begin="8457500000t" end="8499500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">我还想和两位在一起 多工作一阵子</p>
<p begin="8504600000t" end="8532500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">我也是 我也一样</p>
<p begin="8564800000t" end="8581400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">对不起 玛鲁鲁库</p>
<p begin="8605100000t" end="8652100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">还不知身在奈落之底的妈妈 如今怎么样了</p>
<p begin="8660800000t" end="8697300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">所以 也不知道需不需要抓紧赶路</p>
<p begin="8704200000t" end="8735100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">因为不知道 所以必须走快点</p>
<p begin="8739600000t" end="8755000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">是吗</p>
<p begin="8822500000t" end="8855000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">那今天就多聊聊吧</p>
<p begin="8858600000t" end="8893600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">毕竟师尊也是这样吩咐我的</p>
<p begin="9075500000t" end="9091300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">小便…</p>
<p begin="9329500000t" end="9342900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">奥森小姐？</p>
<p begin="9575000000t" end="9590000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">有人在这里吗</p>
<p begin="10026100000t" end="10051900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">那是什么东西啊</p>
<p begin="10178200000t" end="10224000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">没事啦莉可 我也直到前年都会这样</p>
<p begin="10225900000t" end="10269000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">不过莉可 为什么会尿到我的床上来啊</p>
<p begin="10291600000t" end="10316500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">我本来是想去上厕所的</p>
<p begin="10322900000t" end="10376800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">但是 夜里起来去找厕所时 我看到了</p>
<p begin="10413690000t" end="10443390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">就像是另一个世界的生物</p>
<p begin="10463690000t" end="10496800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">我害怕得要命</p>
<p begin="10510500000t" end="10539900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">就躲到雷古的被子里去了 于是就…</p>
<p begin="10555300000t" end="10571900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">真是的 莉可</p>
<p begin="10575400000t" end="10610200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">监视基地不存在那样的怪谈啦</p>
<p begin="10575400000t" end="10610200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">Seeker Camp</p>
<p begin="10610200000t" end="10623700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">但…但是…</p>
<p begin="10623700000t" end="10639000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">就是啊 莉可</p>
<p begin="10640800000t" end="10649500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">雷古？</p>
<p begin="10649500000t" end="10678600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">那…那种脱离现实的…</p>
<p begin="10678600000t" end="10719600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">应该存在吧 长得很像尸体的生物</p>
<p begin="10724800000t" end="10755400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">连妈妈的信件里都没有那种东西啊</p>
<p begin="10790200000t" end="10803000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">师尊</p>
<p begin="10806800000t" end="10838100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">似乎在聊很有趣的事情啊</p>
<p begin="10846700000t" end="10860200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">那…那个</p>
<p begin="10860200000t" end="10882000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">这是我…对不起</p>
<p begin="10896800000t" end="10914400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">哦 是吗</p>
<p begin="10914400000t" end="10941300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">并不是你没有发觉</p>
<p begin="10949900000t" end="10995700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">而是连那小鬼和哈勃尔格 都没听说这件事啊</p>
<p begin="11010600000t" end="11036300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">请问…这是什么意思…</p>
<p begin="11067000000t" end="11083300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">想知道吗</p>
<p begin="11118400000t" end="11147800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">那就跟我来吧</p>
<p begin="11158400000t" end="11201100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">不然的话 就忘记你看到的一切吧</p>
<p begin="11291500000t" end="11301000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">雷古…</p>
<p begin="11456200000t" end="11496200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">你们的事情 我今早听玛鲁鲁库说过了</p>
<p begin="11511200000t" end="11566200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">姑且问一下 你是打算去寻找莱莎的下落吗</p>
<p begin="11569700000t" end="11602700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">是的 因为妈妈在叫我</p>
<p begin="11617900000t" end="11641500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">明明连这个都被送到地面了？</p>
<p begin="11649600000t" end="11669700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">莱莎已经死了</p>
<p begin="11679200000t" end="11721500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">你的寻母之旅 就在这里结束了</p>
<p begin="11749400000t" end="11798100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">奥森小姐是在哪里 发现那枚笛子和信件的？</p>
<p begin="11808200000t" end="11821500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">坟墓</p>
<p begin="11844000000t" end="11870200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">忘了是多少天以前</p>
<p begin="11872700000t" end="11944200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">在四层·巨人之杯深处的一片永恒香花田</p>
<p begin="11948800000t" end="11984200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">那里多了一座坟墓</p>
<p begin="12025900000t" end="12063500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">莱莎生前很喜欢那个地方</p>
<p begin="12092200000t" end="12104300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">怎么会…</p>
<p begin="12109700000t" end="12134400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">但是 是妈妈让我去找她…</p>
<p begin="12134400000t" end="12165000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">那不是莱莎的笔迹</p>
<p begin="12183000000t" end="12226000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">虽然不知道为什么会混进这种字条</p>
<p begin="12229700000t" end="12267000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">但莱莎就算是开玩笑 也不会写出那种字</p>
<p begin="12291300000t" end="12352100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">说来 你去奈落之底 是为了什么来着？</p>
<p begin="12364900000t" end="12394600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">我…我要亲自去证实…</p>
<p begin="12394600000t" end="12444700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">好主意啊 你是想把坟挖开瞧瞧吗</p>
<p begin="12452800000t" end="12463000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">而且…</p>
<p begin="12470700000t" end="12504700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">信里写的神秘人影 或许也跟雷古有关</p>
<p begin="12570500000t" end="12589800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">原来如此啊</p>
<p begin="12787300000t" end="12800000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">这是什么地方</p>
<p begin="12810100000t" end="12824700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">我的房间</p>
<p begin="12836600000t" end="12865000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">你们不是想知道 才跟来的吗</p>
<p begin="12956400000t" end="12972700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">进来吧</p>
<p begin="13314300000t" end="13368100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">空に浮かんでる 光る波を</p>
<p begin="13314300000t" end="13368100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">将浮映在半空中的 光之波纹</p>
<p begin="13368100000t" end="13420200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">束ねて虹の 橋を掛けよう</p>
<p begin="13368100000t" end="13420200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">都收集到一起 挂在虹桥上吧</p>
<p begin="13420200000t" end="13473600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">危うい足場 滑るスロープ</p>
<p begin="13420200000t" end="13473600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">险峻的道路 湿滑的斜坡</p>
<p begin="13473600000t" end="13519500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">過去と未来の道標</p>
<p begin="13473600000t" end="13519500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">是标记着过去与未来的路标</p>
<p begin="13526200000t" end="13572900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">君の左手 僕の右手を</p>
<p begin="13526200000t" end="13572900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">将你的左手 我的右手</p>
<p begin="13575400000t" end="13625400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">繋いで 繋げて はじめよう</p>
<p begin="13575400000t" end="13625400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">紧紧相握 牢牢相系 一同出发吧</p>
<p begin="13631700000t" end="13653000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">いつもそばにいるよ</p>
<p begin="13631700000t" end="13653000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">我会始终与你在一起</p>
<p begin="13658000000t" end="13678800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">過去も今も未来も</p>
<p begin="13658000000t" end="13678800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">无论过去未来或如今</p>
<p begin="13680900000t" end="13757200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">だから迷わずに歩いていこう</p>
<p begin="13680900000t" end="13757200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">所以不要迷茫 一起迈出脚步吧</p>
<p begin="13764300000t" end="13823100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">色とりどりの夢 重ねて</p>
<p begin="13764300000t" end="13823100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">将色彩斑斓的梦 重叠在一起</p>
<p begin="13829400000t" end="13866500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">明日はどこに向かう</p>
<p begin="13829400000t" end="13866500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">明天的我们 该前往何方？</p>
<p begin="13869400000t" end="13929100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">君と一緒にいれたら</p>
<p begin="13869400000t" end="13929100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">只要与你彼此相伴</p>
<p begin="13932000000t" end="13970400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">世界は輝きだすよ</p>
<p begin="13932000000t" end="13970400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">世界便会绽放光芒</p>
<p begin="13973700000t" end="14049600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">最果ての地に咲く花を探そう</p>
<p begin="13973700000t" end="14049600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">去寻找绽放在大地尽头的花朵吧</p>
<p begin="14169300000t" end="14210600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">下集</p>
